* They should be administered a high dose of Solution HU17Z1L.[[footnote]]An hallucinogen and rage-inducing chemical cocktail containing adrenaline, cocaine, and //amanita muscaria//. A high dose induces a violent trance-like state. [[/footnote]]
* The subjects must be brought to the //temalácatl//[[footnote]]Mesoamerican gladiatorial arena[[/footnote]] in front of SCP-7279-Ce. They should be positioned facing each other on the opposite extreme of the //temalácatl//. Two //macuahuimeh//[[footnote]]Plural of //macuahuitl//: a sword or club of wood with obsidian blades [[/footnote]] shall be left at their feet.

